      "comment_id" : 129590356,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "To keep in mind. \\@Validated doesn&#39;t validate nested DTOs, you need to put \\@Valid on those nested fields (Account#user for example) in order to propagate validation for them."
