    "question_id" : 36173332,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just for simplifying:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>@Validated</code> annotation is a class-level annotation that we can use to tell <code>Spring</code> to validate parameters that are passed into a method of the annotated class.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>and</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>@Valid</code> annotation on method parameters and fields to tell <code>Spring</code> that we want a method parameter or field to be validated.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
