    "creation_date" : 1707052619,
    "answer_id" : 77935937,
    "question_id" : 36173332,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>@Validated</code> at the class level of <code>@Controller</code>/<code>@RestController</code> is used to validate the <code>@PathVariable</code>/<code>@RequestParam</code> parameters</p>\n<p>While <code>@Valid</code> won't work for <code>@PathVariable</code>/<code>@RequestParam</code> parameters</p>\n<p>If validation fails for <code>@PathVariable</code>/<code>@RequestParam</code> it throws <code>ConstraintViolationException</code></p>\n"
  } ],
